name: Hair on Womens Clutch Wallet - Tan/Gold
description:
The outer vegtable tanned leather of this wallet has been laminated with specailty gold foiled hair on cow skin. Why laminated? By bringing these two layers together it makes is far more durable and stonger to last for years.

All the layers have been handstitched together using saddle stitch with waxed linen thread. This type of stitch ensures the item will hold together no matter what you throw at it.

This stunning wallet clutch is best used everyday. This wallet opens completely flat and has 3 long pockets for cash and receipts, 1 large zippered pocket for coins, 10 card pockets including a clear faced pocket for your family photo or drivers licence it has everything you need. The lining is made of choc brown leather.

The t bar close is a gun metal colour with a great thread through and flip up or down latch for ease of use.

Care is minimal at the nutrally occuring oils in the cow skin will repel most stains.

Measures 
Closed
19cm wide
11cm Tall

Open
22.5cm tall
19cm wide

name: Sophia Leather bag in Foxy Tan
description:
A timeless slouch style that is sleek, elegant and fun. It will always make an impact with the colours of her heart.

Created from 100% Anilene Vegtable tanned leather Sophia is so soft sumptious and smells great.

Features a custom laser cut belt leather strap with engraving 1 1/2inch wide. Attached to the bag with 4 screws on each side. Having the typical characteristics of a belt, they start out a little tough but with love and use turn to a soft and supple companion. 

The lining is a light weight upholstery fabric that is a hsunny yellow with a white geometric pattern to bring a smile to your face as well as equiped with a zippered pocket on one side and a double slip pocket on the other.

This bag secures with a magnetic snap aswell as its folded design for extra security.

All BHO leather bags are "FOREVER" bags. They are made to last years not seasons and designed to be incredibly functional. Buy a BHO leather bag and you are sure to love it for years to come.

Measures 
Wide 33cm 
Tall 26cm 
Deep 12cm

Strap from shoulder to bag is 40cm appx due to the slouch design each bag is a little different.

This Item is made from quality full anilene leather please note this item has a matte finished with visible grain and unique details. For more information please see the What Leather and Why tab at the top of the page.

These handy two pocket pockets can get you organised and on the go. The carry all with wrist strap is large enough to hold your phone! Even an iphone 5 with a case on. While the front pocket remains free for your cash and cards. If you like to be super organised you can use the poppys pouch to keep your coins wrangled and you credit cards in check.

Quality hardware, machine and handstitching elements ensure a durable purse that will stand the test of time.

Large Carry All is
Wide 16cm
Tall 10cm

Poppys Pouch
Wide 11cm
Tall 7cm

This Item is made from quality full anilene leather please note this item has a matte finished with visible grain and unique details. For more information please see the What Leather and Why tab at the top of the page.

name: 3 Pocket Totes - Kelly Green and Pearl White
description:
New to the BHO forever collection is the 3 pocket tote.
This is a one of a kind piece.

Unlined and created with sumptious full anilene leather, they are the best of both worlds exposing the gorgeous suede and smooth sides of the hide.

They feature 3 slip pockets of which one is the front screen printed panel then their are 2 inside the bag that are 4" deep high up perfect for phones and keys.

The straps are made from 2 pieces of leather for strength then stitched together for durability. They are secured though 4 layers of leather with a screw and post system,

The tote is top stitched reinforcing the leather pockets to the bag.

Tote measures
Wide 31cm
Tall 36cm
Depth 5cm
Handle length 24cm (from tip of handle to top of bag)

This Item is made from quality full anilene leather please note this item has a matte finished with visible grain and unique details. For more information please see the What Leather and Why tab at the top of the page.

name: Sophia Leather bag in Yellow Sunshine
description:
A timeless slouch style that is sleek, elegant and fun. It will always make an impact with the colours of her heart.

Created from 100% Anilene Vegtable tanned leather Sophia is so soft sumptious and smells great.

Features a custom laser cut belt leather strap with engraving 1 1/2inch wide. Attached to the bag with 4 screws on each side. Having the typical characteristics of a belt, they start out a little tough but with love and use turn to a soft and supple companion. 

The lining is a light weight upholstery fabric that is a happy duck egg blue with a white geometric pattern to bring a smile to your face as well as equiped with a zippered pocket on one side and a double slip pocket on the other.

This bag secures with a magnetic snap aswell as its folded design for extra security.

All BHO leather bags are "FOREVER" bags. They are made to last years not seasons and designed to be incredibly functional. Buy a BHO leather bag and you are sure to love it for years to come.

Measures 
Wide 33cm 
Tall 26cm 
Deep 12cm

Strap from shoulder to bag is 40cm appx due to the slouch design each bag is a little different.

This Item is made from quality full anilene leather please note this item has a matte finished with visible grain and unique details. For more information please see the What Leather and Why tab at the top of the page.

name: NEW Fabric Wallet in Cubix
description:
These beautiful wallets hold between 5 and 15 cards in slots that can be triple stacked. Your notes will lay flat behind the zippered coin pocket leaving the card section free for loyalty cards, receipts or even your mobile phone!

BHO wallets are all completely machine washable, just pop them into the washing machine on a cold setting with similar colours and dry flat.

Each wallet is individually quilt stitched to not only ensure durability but to hold all the layers together so the wallet will always retain it’s shape.

BHO wallets feature an elastic lasoo closure that ensures no matter how much you put into your wallet it will always close.

Each wallet feature a Porcelain button designed exclusively for BHO.

Wallet Measures 
Closed 
18.5cm wide 
10cm tall

Open 
18.5cm wide 
21cm tall

*Note: Fabric Pattern Placement may vary.

name: Hair On! Clutch Wallet - Lambs Wool
description:
HAIR ON!

The outer vegtable tanned leather of this wallet has been laminated with hair on lambs wool. Why laminated? By bringing these two layers together it makes is far more durable and stonger to last for years.

All the layers including the lining have been whip stitched together using a waxed linen thread.

This stunning wallet clutch is best used everyday. This wallet opens completely flat and has 3 long pockets for cash and receipts, 1 large zippered pocket for coins, 10 card pockets including a clear faced pocket for your family photo or drivers licence it has everything you need. The lining is made of choc brown leather.

The t bar close is a gun metal colour with a great thread through and flip up or down latch for ease of use.

Care is minimal at the naturally occuring oils in the hair will repel most stains.

Measures 
Closed
19cm wide
11cm Tall

Open
22.5cm tall
19cm wide

name: Handstitched and custom dyed leather backpack - Black
description:
This sumptious forever bag began life as a raw piece of leather. It has been dyed and hand stitched into this sumptious and sleek backpack.

Who said back packs could not be stylish! From its black suede draw string close, pewter rivets and silver hardware even the savvy shopper can enjoy the sophistication this backpack oozes.

The internal pocket snaps in and out of the interior to make it oh so flexible and easily accessed.
